FYI, you need to modify tensorflow/contrib/android/jni/version_script.lds

VERS_1.0 {
  # Export JNI symbols.
  global:
    Java_*;
    JNI_OnLoad;
    JNI_OnUnload;
+    *TF_*;
+    *TFE_*;

  # Hide everything else.
  local:
    *;
};
